01:07.355 --> 01:10.538
This is the holy and inspired word of God.

01:13.881 --> 01:26.034
And you were dead in the trespasses and sins in which you once walked following the course of this world, following the prince of the power of the air, the spirit that is now at work in the sons of disobedience.

01:27.170 --> 01:41.433
Among whom we all once lived in the passions of our flesh, carrying out the desires of the body and the mind and were by nature children of wrath, like the rest of mankind.

01:43.056 --> 01:54.514
But God, being rich in mercy, because of the great love with which He loved us, even when we were dead in our trespasses.

01:55.682 --> 01:58.185
made us alive together with Christ.

01:58.706 --> 02:06.855
By grace, you have been saved and raised us up with him and seated us with him in the heavenly places in Christ Jesus.

02:08.197 --> 02:23.314
So that in the coming ages, he might show the immeasurable riches of his grace in kindness toward us in Christ Jesus.

02:24.482 --> 02:26.264
Amen, this is the word of the Lord.

02:26.584 --> 02:28.066
May he bless us to us, let's pray.

02:29.927 --> 02:48.405
Our Father in heaven, what we have not give to us, what we know not, teach us what we are not, make of us, and we ask that you would do so through the grace that is in Christ Jesus.

02:49.527 --> 02:53.010
