03:15.358 --> 03:20.626
The way he's been putting it of late is that, well, Jesus died.

03:20.866 --> 03:39.373
And Jesus rose, and Jesus ascended, and Jesus is seated at the right hand of the majesty on high, and you, by God's power at work in you, you have been bound to Christ in His death, resurrection, ascension, and heavenly session.

03:40.454 --> 03:48.466
And so God gave you spiritual life in Jesus, and that life will go on forever.

03:48.546 --> 03:52.212
Maybe you remember in a different context, Jesus talking about this.

03:52.312 --> 03:59.384
When Nicodemus came to him at night, that teacher in Israel wanted to ask Jesus some questions.

03:59.464 --> 04:08.639
And Jesus said to him in John chapter three, Nicodemus, unless you are born again, you cannot see the kingdom of God.

04:08.879 --> 04:10.802
You cannot see the kingdom of heaven.

04:11.106 --> 04:12.668
