08:59.867 --> 09:01.549
Why did God make you alive in Christ?

09:01.629 --> 09:02.930
So Christian, because

09:03.394 --> 09:09.603
First, because of his rich mercy, verse four, but God being rich in mercy.

09:10.504 --> 09:18.215
